        <ontology:hasDescription>The reference mountain chain of this VC is Slovak Carpathians. The reference mountain landscape of this VC is Hozelec. Hozelec is a small municipality located between two small villages Gánovce and Švábovce. There is a direct view on the High Tatras (the highest mountains in Slovakia). The district city Poprad is located 5km away.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


